*beep-media-player-0.9.7-r1 (19 Dec 2004)

  19 Dec 2004; Tony Vroon <chainsaw@gentoo.org> metadata.xml,
  +files/0.9.7-noclick-resize.patch, +beep-media-player-0.9.7-r1.ebuild:
  Added upstream patch for playlist doubleclick segfault, closes bug #73297.
  MP3 support now a USE-flag. Took maintainership.

  17 Dec 2004; Tony Vroon <chainsaw@gentoo.org>
  beep-media-player-0.9.7.ebuild:
  Stable on x86 for better plugin stability.

*beep-media-player-0.9.7 (16 Dec 2004)

